                    <b>Highlights</b><br><br><b>Drivers cab:</b><br><br>swivel driver''s seat<br><br><b>Automotive body:</b><br><br>Detachable backhoe loading unit with fold-down support legs (can be locked in two positions - work and drive position)<br>Folding support legs and tread tyres<br>Frontloading shovel with loading and unloading position<br>Fully functional backhoe loader<br>Changeable front loader scoop<br><br><b>Chassis:</b><br><br>All-terrain oscillating axle<br><br><b>Motion/function:</b><br><br>Changeable backhoe loader scoop<br><br><b>Common:</b><br><br>Compatible with figure<br>Recommended age: suitable from 3 years upwards for playing indoors and outdoors<br>Received Spiel Gut Award; for more information, visit spielgut.org<br>Manufactured from high-quality plastics such as ABS<br>Made in Germany<br>Scale 1:16<br><br><b>Description</b><br><br>The 50HP backhoe loader with a speed of 26 km/h, distinguished by leading specialist journalists with the demopark Gold Medal, is small, agile and can be equipped with classic farming implements. It can be used on large and small construction sites and combines 3 tools in one: a mini digger, a compact wheel loader and a compact tractor. <br><br>This innovative concept makes it an ideal tool for landscaping as well as for completing a wide range of communal tasks in civil engineering. The versatile work options are reproduced in the true-to-the-original BRUDER model. For this reason it actually has a fully functional (and detachable) front shovel as well as a fully usable and detachable backhoe loading unit with one-handed operation. <br><br>Two fold-in support legs give the backhoe loader stability, the floating axle for every terrain and tread tyres complete the picture. The backhoe loader can be provided with a standard tractor coupling to add to the fun of playing when the front end loader is detached which enables all trailers and equipment of the farming series to be used.
